*DESCRIPTION_START
This room is in construction.  The end goal is to have all the temp
scripts and other various variables accessible through here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER Hey! You're here in the control room, but the main content isn't loaded yet.
