CALL 18
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is the patio of the 'shoe. Various brandnames adorn the
canopies of the table umbrellas. A separate smaller bar is out
here with about 20 taps. A door leads inside the pub and the
stairway leads to the second floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 65 VAL2=1910 UNLOCKED
ITEM 1 81 VAL2=1911
;
NUMBER 483
NAME Room-o-marking
ASTRAL
IFPREVERB XYZZY -1
	IFVAR INTNUM3 = 0
		EQUAL INTNUM3 PVAL12
	    ADD PVAL12 1
  STRCVT 0 INTNUM3
		GMMSG ***** %N is INTNUM3 of %0.
    ELSE
  STRCVT 0 INTNUM3
    	GMMSG ** %N is already INTNUM3 of %0.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
